BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Menopause is not a disease - it is a natural transition. But that doesn't mean it's easy.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (Hot flashes, sleep disruption, mood changes, weight gain, and brain fog can significantly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (impact your quality of life. This guide gives you practical tools to navigate this) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (transition with knowledge and grace.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
