BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 1: Understanding Menopause) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (The Stages of Menopause) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 652.2 Td (Perimenopause \(2-10 years before menopause\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.2 Td (- Hormones begin fluctuating wildly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 622.2 Td (- Periods become irregular) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.2 Td (- Symptoms often begin here \(many women don't realize\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.2 Td (- Can start as early as late 30s, typically mid-40s) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 576.2 Td (Menopause \(defined retrospectively\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.2 Td (- 12 consecutive months without a period) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.2 Td (- Average age: 51 \(range 45-55\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 528.2 Td (Postmenopause \(after\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512.2 Td (- Symptoms may continue for years) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.2 Td (- Focus shifts to long-term health \(bones, heart, brain\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 468.4 Td (Common Symptoms) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 450.4 Td (- Hot flashes and night sweats \(75% of women\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 436.4 Td (- Sleep disturbances) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 422.4 Td (- Mood changes \(anxiety, irritability, depression\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 408.4 Td (- Brain fog and memory issues) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 394.4 Td (- Weight gain \(especially midsection\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.4 Td (- Vaginal dryness and painful intimacy) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366.4 Td (- Joint pain and stiffness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.4 Td (- Thinning hair and skin changes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 338.4 Td (- Heart palpitations) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 324.4 Td (- Urinary changes) Tj ET
endstream
