BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Exercise for Menopause) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Exercise becomes even more critical during menopause for bone density, muscle mass,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (metabolic health, mood, and sleep.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Strength training: 2-3x/week \(builds bone and muscle\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (- Weight-bearing cardio: Walking, dancing, hiking) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.2 Td (- Flexibility: Yoga, stretching \(joint health\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.2 Td (- Balance work: Prevents falls as bone density changes) Tj ET
