98 0 obj
<< /Length 2386 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: At what age does menopause start?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Average age is 51, but perimenopause can begin 4-10 years earlier. The normal range for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (menopause is 45-55. Before 45 is considered early menopause.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.4 Td (Q: Is HRT safe?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (For most healthy women under 60 or within 10 years of menopause, HRT benefits outweigh) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (risks. Individual risk factors matter. Have a thorough discussion with your doctor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 560.6 Td (Q: Will I gain weight during menopause?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (Metabolic changes make weight gain easier, but it's not inevitable. Prioritize strength) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (training, protein intake, and be aware that you may need fewer calories than before.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (Q: How long do hot flashes last?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (Average duration is 7-10 years, but varies widely. Some women have them for a few months,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (others for 20+ years. Treatment can significantly reduce frequency and severity.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 445.0 Td (Q: Can I get pregnant during perimenopause?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 429.0 Td (Yes! Until you've had 12 months without a period, pregnancy is possible. Use contraception) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 415.0 Td (if pregnancy is not desired.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 387.2 Td (Q: Does menopause affect mental health?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 371.2 Td (Yes. Fluctuating hormones can trigger anxiety, depression, irritability, and brain fog.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357.2 Td (These are physiological, not 'just stress.' Treatment is available and effective.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 329.4 Td (Q: What about vaginal dryness?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 313.4 Td (Very common and treatable. Options include local estrogen \(very safe\), moisturizers, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 299.4 Td (lubricants. Don't suffer in silence - talk to your doctor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 271.6 Td (Q: Should I get a bone density test?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 255.6 Td (Generally recommended at age 65, or earlier if you have risk factors \(early menopause,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 241.6 Td (family history, low body weight, smoking, certain medications\).) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
